"download the subscription portal with a separate Front-end servers, from CDN"
" or directly from the device firmware (the so-called *fat* client) because "
"it only consist of static files or developed in the native language of the "
"device. With the server Back-end and subscriber applications communicate via"
" JSON or XML-RPC API."

